even though it's not a professional team.

25
00:00:57,807 --> 00:01:01,227
-What's the point?
-You know I like passing out at night.

26
00:01:01,311 --> 00:01:03,146
-Exercise is good for you, and it's fun.
-Right.

27
00:01:03,229 --> 00:01:06,357
You pass out and never hang out.
A man gets lonely!

28
00:01:06,441 --> 00:01:09,319
Come on, Yun-sang.
We're always together at night.

29
00:01:09,402 --> 00:01:12,113
-What?
-Don't need that information, Se-kyung.

30
00:01:12,197 --> 00:01:15,116
-Whoa! Keep those stories to yourself.
-There's a child here!

31
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:17,994
How dare you!
That's not what I said at all.

32
00:01:18,703 --> 00:01:20,371
I didn't mean that!

33
00:01:20,455 --> 00:01:22,874
About your wedding…
It's gotta be coming up.

34
00:01:22,957 --> 00:01:23,875
I'll be officiating.

35
00:01:23,958 --> 00:01:26,127
Please do!
Thank you in advance.

36
00:01:26,211 --> 00:01:28,546
-Hello, Father.
-Oh, hello.

37
00:01:28,630 --> 00:01:30,131
-Thank you.
-Hi.

38
